{"tid":1264740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成班以為尻叫尻罵就係抗爭","createTime":"2019-06-28T22:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T23:31:39.000Z","uid":96780,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"539dab5e02dd32d690431d7004fadc2c57a214e3","tid":1264740,"uid":96780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:08:21.000Z","msg":"真係無眼睇落去<br />\n班人到底明唔明一開始贏緊既原因係D咩<br />\n一開波和平示威比警犬暴力清場<br />\n得到媒體同埋社會各勢力同情先至可以行到咁耐<br />\n但近期又搞尻TVB記者 打壓新聞自由 圍警總搞尻大肚婆<br />\n而家民意開始逆轉<br />\n成班咪繼續自我感覺良好地罵囉 根本有班人就係為左搞事而唔係抗爭<br />\n大家認住今日尻叫尻罵果班人<br />\n第時輸左 就係呢班人累事既<br />\n一個二個聽到唔同意見 又屌晒鬼話人分化又剩<br />\n真心覺得呢班人同以前紅衛兵一D分別都無<br />\n只不過佢地今次包裝成民主同自由既外表 骨子裡其實係一樣既"},{"pid":"e5a61111dfae94872ede7ee1ac27e06d237b757e","tid":1264740,"uid":27664,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:16:46.000Z","msg":"點會輸呢，民主路上 二十幾年都冇贏過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a888f78ea35a3028b696bfcd072df59ff016e7bb","tid":1264740,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛剛看到，希望大家都能讓心情慢下來，有思考的空間。"},{"pid":"b6c7d90b168a90b6ad65c2888fee89c59e46e209","tid":1264740,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T22:59:12.000Z","msg":"各有各做呀屌你老母<br />\n唔支持都唔好指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /